website_summaries.verdict: A moderately priced, well-rounded formula that provides a balanced diet from clean ingredients. Squash, berries and pumpkin seeds round out the natural proteins.
pros: Made with chicken and salmon that's free from antibiotics, hormones and steroids
Meat complemented by organic produce and minerals
Balanced amino acid, fatty acid and enzyme levels
cons: Food comes in large nuggets which can be challenging to re-hydrate, and some cats find the dry nuggets hard to eat

customer_reviews.title: Cats don't like it
customer_reviews.text: At first, all 4 of my cats were excited about this food, but I soon realized it was just because it was "new" food to them. Like most cats, they get excited about getting something different to eat. After 2 times, only 2 of the 4 were still interested in this food. Then, those 2 cats started throwing up this food and neither are prone to puking. I stopped feeding it to them and will not purchase again.

customer_reviews.title: Dogs and Cats Need Raw
customer_reviews.text: Results: Healthy, happy, energetic cat with beautiful velvet fur. Cats and dogs need raw. They do not thrive on processed kibble -- in fact, we're killing our animals by feeding them that crap. Switch out the flavors for variety, but stick with a good brand when you find it. I have revived over a dozen rescued animals with the raw diet. Do it right if you care. Save on vet bills!
customer_reviews.author: Lizzie BigWings

customer_reviews.title: Supreme Product
customer_reviews.text: My cat loves this...when I mix it with a teaspoon of powdered goat milk. I noticed a major change in her disposition since I switched her breakfast and lunch to raw food. She is much friendlier and relaxed. I also noticed some weight loss which is good because she gained a lot after she was spayed. This food actually lasts awhile and is worth the money in my opinion. It requires a little more prep work then just scooping wet food out of a can but I think it’s well worth the effort since it’s for her health. After all, in nature cats eat raw food...seems to be working for her!

product_meta.title: Primal Pet Foods Freeze-Dried Feline Chicken And Salmon Formula 5.5 Oz
product_meta.description: Primal Chicken & Salmon Formula Nuggets Grain-Free Raw Freeze-Dried Cat Food offers your hungry kitty all the benefits of a safe and wholesome raw-food diet—without you having to grind, chop, measure or mix the ingredients yourself! Taking great pride to source only the best ingredients, this tasty and nutritious diet is packed with naturally derived vitamins and minerals. The high-protein ratio appeals to your feline friend’s primal diet, and it’s an excellent way to maintain a proper weight and boost overall health. And best of all, it’s a breeze to serve, thanks to the naturally preserved nuggets—just add water! The proof comes in watching him lick the bowl clean while thriving happily and healthfully.
